      <title>Memorandum</title>
      <para id="id12389764">Groupwork:</para>
      <para id="id11313040"><emphasis effect="bold">Observation: </emphasis>The glowing wooden splinter catches fire because oxygen has been released.</para>
      <para id="id12418201"><emphasis effect="bold">Conclusion: </emphasis>Mercury oxide is a compound that decomposed as a result of heating. It broke up into oxygen (a gas) and mercury (a metal).</para>
      <para id="id11805969">Mercury Oxide = mercury + oxygen</para>
