    <section id="id7857476">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id12177178"><emphasis>Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis>The learner will be able to act confidently on curiosity about natural phenomena, and to investigate relationships and solve problems in scientific, technological and environmental contexts.</para>
      <para id="id13427280"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 1.2:</emphasis> We know this when the learner conducts investigations and collects data: organises and uses apparatus/equipment or sources to gain and record information;</para>
      <para id="id13427264"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 1.3:</emphasis> We know this when the learner evaluates data and communicates findings: generalises in terms of relevant aspects and describes how the data support the generalisation.</para>
